comment:
* Wrapper for Transport Discovery Data Transport Blocks. This class represents a Transport Block
 * from a Transport Discovery Data.
 *
 * @see TransportDiscoveryData
 * @see AdvertiseData

methods.name: public void writeToParcel(@NonNull Parcel dest, int flags)
public int getOrgId()
methods.comment:
* Gets the Organization ID of the Transport Block which corresponds to one of the Bluetooth SIG
     * Assigned Numbers.

methods.name: public int getTdsFlags()
methods.comment:
* Gets the TDS flags of the Transport Block which represents the role of the device and
     * information about its state and supported features.

methods.name: public int getTransportDataLength()
methods.comment: Gets the total number of octets in the Transport Data field in this Transport Block.

methods.name: public byte[] getTransportData()
methods.comment: Gets the Transport Data of the Transport Block which contains organization-specific data.

methods.name: public byte[] toByteArray()
methods.comment:
* Converts this TransportBlock to byte array
     *
     * @return byte array representation of this Transport Block or null if the conversion failed

methods.name: public int totalBytes()
methods.comment: * @return total byte count of this TransportBlock
